metadata.name: ALL SEEING
metadata.description:
2 / 2

Amidst the storm of adversity, a woman found solace in her most cherished trinket, a delicate eye-shaped pendant. Its golden gaze seemed to hold the strength she yearned for. Life had been relentless, leaving scars on her spirit, but she clung to her talisman, knowing it held her resilience within. Each day, as she fastened the pendant around her neck, she would whisper, "I am strong." The eye became her guiding light, reminding her of the courage hidden within her soul. And in her darkest hours, she would touch its smooth surface, drawing strength from the belief that she could weather any storm that came her way.

Trinkets, a collection to be about cherishing those things that are most precious and beautiful to you. Showing strength to survive the tough times.
